{"tid":2195659,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"太陽從西環升起 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-09-09T10:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:17:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc8f90f92804449e5edb9ed42d22b46a3e605ea","tid":2195659,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200909/O2BC7JHQQFDEBMG4PTAN3RV2F4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200909%2FO2BC7JHQQFDEBMG4PTAN3RV2F4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgzmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=ff4207e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200909%2FO2BC7JHQQFDEBMG4PTAN3RV2F4%2F&h=43102068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200909/O2BC7JHQQFDEBMG4PTAN3RV2F4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n太陽從西環升起 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WmYykHFf60gTctO0ERD_GAiDSV4=/4348x2900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KKKIYXL6TFDHXG3H2WMM7PAYAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWmYykHFf60gTctO0ERD_GAiDSV4%3D%2F4348x2900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKKKIYXL6TFDHXG3H2WMM7PAYAI.jpg&h=06c41b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環咆哮，決不允許香港再亂起來。<br />\n<br />\n紅眼了，要下殺着嗎？明斯克政權即刻借用，泰國政府請西環過兩招使吓。馬克龍總統也要請教，黃背心仍然讓政府眼眉跳啊。侵侵呢？出動過國民警衛軍，煽動侵粉中的極右槍械狂周街練靶，仍然無法切斷美國各州的示威浪潮鏈。侵侵咁惡都辦不來，西環「旗鼓相當」，叻過侵侵，國際拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n香港這邊，四個黑警將十二歲少女撞飛再按壓在地，香港就不再亂起來？西環加碼針對中學生，限制出街嗎？泰國軍政府試過了，中學生依然拎住白紙上街抗議。對黑警的藐視，與生俱來，未出世已經感受懷孕的母親遭黑警推跌的新品種香港人，會被「決不允許」嚇倒？無條件跪低？向極權犯下的暴行掩埋良心說「微不足道」？<br />\n<br />\n決不允許再亂，得嘅，人為又好天意又好，讓武肺變種襲港，人人自危，鬧市變死城，亂個屁咩。。。。。。。"}]}